\centerline{$\hat{\delta}_{OLS} = \hat{\Delta^Y_{WWOLS(X)}}$}}

\noindent{So I get the OLS estimator $\bm{\hat{\delta}_{OLS} = \hat{\Delta^Y_{WWOLS(X)}}=\Sexpr{tt}$.}

